            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and roughly chop your <strong>onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into wedges</p><p>Deseed your <strong>sweet pointed pepper[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thick strips</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-54-1725454342909-x200.jpg",
