          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-54-1725454342909-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>onion wedges</strong> to the dish with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong>, your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and<strong> half </strong>your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground coriander</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>dried oregano </strong>and <strong>half </strong>your <strong>smoked paprika </strong>with 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[475ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>,<strong> </strong>your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-56-1725454348113-x200.jpg",
