            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, return the <strong>pork belly </strong>to the dish, skin-side up</p><p>Put the dish in the oven and cook, uncovered, for an initial 30 min</p><p>Wash your <strong>rocket</strong>,<strong> </strong>pat dry with kitchen paper and set aside</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-56-1725454352371-x200.jpg",
