          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-55-1725454355907-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>crispy pork belly</strong> from the dish and cut into 3 <strong>slices </strong>per person</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>remaining white wine vinegar </strong>and a little <strong>olive oil </strong>over the <strong>washed rocket</strong></p><p>To serve, top the <strong>smoky sauce</strong> with the <strong>pork belly slices</strong> and the <strong>dressed rocket</strong> and set the dish in the centre of the table with the<strong> wedges </strong>to the side</p><p>Let everyone dig in!</p>",
